{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"Z.C.C","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay3v1KwhY3Bw2BzLLhiboZ35ibRbvCXAIxZ4hzca31e4dHxKN6SWlp0pH212JhzyDFHKJC9C40d8tVq/0","content":"1.由于人民币贬值风险的加剧，部分国内投资者开始了解境外资产配置，包括债券类的投资，还在房产和境外保险。<div>2.包含美元在内的海外投资产品，由于门槛较高，受众小，周期长，把握走势难度大，并且有项目退出和资金回流的危险，所以望大众谨慎购买。</div><div>3.境外的保险产品比较稳妥，国内居民可以考虑选择<br><div><br></div></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":9086,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492789571000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"涂健辉","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6975DaiacvApR9TiajQPuzmMpibpzfBmxy72xDkxVa9SxAYwHiaWHFxdia3cliajsE6N9yMxuibibLpN8QJgPyiaFBzwsQ7b/0","content":"购买美元理财产品比购买人民币理财产品收益率要高，但如果只是短期持有美元，高昂的手续费可能抵消换汇收益。<div>自2015年起，有部分投资者关注到人民币可能有贬值风险，已开始了解境外资产的配置。主要包括海外投资产品、外汇投资类产品和境外保险产品。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":9083,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492789222000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"A俞宣龙","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQFzAK9kBK1D4Y3iam8ZQe8gDicib7BR3ggT45WM7PrrLja8zFcfbUabfKwwIev2n8jpHibhiaCqBv2Tk4/0","content":"现在国内银行的持续低利息和人民币贬值使得我们存在银行里的钱不停的贬值亏本，所以要是手头上有余钱钱可以不放在银行，可以去找一些收益稳定的理财产品来保值和赚取点收益。<div>理财产品可以分国内和国外的理财产品。从整体收益上来说，9月份的数据显示国外理财特别是美元理财产品的整体收益率要高于国内。主要的受益点是汇率产生的价差，虽然有高额的手续费，但是汇率的收益要大的多。</div><div>但是我们投资美元理财产品要注意以下几点。</div><div>1、投资门槛高需要余钱多：a、投资起步价15万起步.b、高额的交易费用投资期限适合长期投资，短期投资不利于收益。c、外汇投资都是长周期的，3-5年左右。</div><div>2、需要懂得汇率：美元理财产品除去汇率影响的实际收益率小于国内的。国内是3.7%，美元是1.57%.美元的收益点是汇率6%的作用，所以要想有收益需要能对汇率有提前了解。</div><div>3、要寻找低风险产品：其中保险类相对稳妥一些，适合在香港配置。</div><div><br></div><div><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":9070,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492787105000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"JET","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaEIdj3GaIwdwOD3wPialIkhtFZtqulYaWnBFVuvBlcRYDibuUhtYAb0HDgoYZ9ibCg6libWs0dzkQka2hQ/0","content":"主题：如何进行资产配置<div>1:海外投资产品门槛高，收益率普遍比国内低<div>2:外汇投资产品周期较长</div><div>3:境外保险投资相对稳定，适合中国内地居民</div></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":9043,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492785308000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"君君君","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/Q3auHgzwzM7VA9siaqMbYPxpsm8taM8kcHctAsQP8lIXASTa1801I7ZqkTcHUmfG3mF1vGB7huA4IibcdpRLajOvATF6WVUMbicM840iaUoUqps/0","content":"当前经济环境下，把钱存在银行的收益追不上物价飞涨的速度，也就是说你把钱存在银行相当于赔钱。<div>2015年初开始，有些敏感的投资者关注到人民币潜在的贬值风险，已经开始主动了解境外的资产的配置。</div><div>在海外投资产品中，美元等投资类产品门槛较高，一般在15万美元以上，且投资期限较长，一般投资期3~4年，加上退出期达4~5年。</div><div>相对而言，境外保险产品比较稳妥一点。与中国内地居民而言，配置香港保险无疑是最佳的选择。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8992,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492775077000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Chloé\uD83C\uDF38","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98VqypG8k613qpXMTOxWCwuEYOlv8biaWvImV5ibtpPfyYuXesHBM3ZGK9iahEsgmCrib0rEPvBFZVwzNypOSP6olVZ2/0","content":"<p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">在国内，把钱存在银行等于是赔钱</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">在国外，购买美元理财产品比购买人民币理财产品收益率要高</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:\nminor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">境外资产配置可以是</span></p><p>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">，外汇投资类</span>——</p><p>a<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">周期长</span></p><p>b<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">有风险（短期近乎无收益，长期利于资产保值）</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">，买境外保险——</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; background-color: transparent;\">a相对稳妥</span></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">香港保险是最佳选择。</span></p><p>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:\n宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">，境外美元投资类产品——</span></p><p>a<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">投入高，</span></p><p>b<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">周期长，</span></p><p>c<span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:\nCalibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin\">收益普遍低于国内理财产品</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8964,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492768998000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"夏九久","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLC7icDQwYiaWaGS6geWFLky3tkr20OnibpPzjFBmm9e0wolRib25XsITs00lhLgyRfkuL2ZtF8XmdJgXw/0","content":"题干的问题有三个，一、对内容分类，二、提炼信息，三、分享。<div>一：分类</div><div>1. 发生的情况：第三段，第四段</div><div>2. 对情况的分析：第一段，第二段，第五段，第六段</div><div>3. 解决办法：第七段</div><div>二：提炼信息</div><div>人民币存在潜在的贬值风险，购买境外理财产品有助于资产保值。购买美元理财产品的收益率比人民币高，但需要投资者有较高的把握外汇走势的能力。其中境外保险产品最为稳妥，对中国内地居民而言，配置香港保险是最佳选择。</div><div>三，分享</div><div>谢谢圈圈姐的分享</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8952,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492767178000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"JAN","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcLTWw0LNeDjZDn1c8WExrczopsr0BKQk0xdG08OeUSXA1kSsHtH2sTIichYJcuBa66G8kjDtibRetLoWCuUxbNzeQ/0","content":"根据央行第四季度维持稳健的货币政策以及CPI增幅放缓的现状可知，把钱存在银行或投资人民币理财产品将难以实现预期高收益。但相较于美元投资产品的换汇手续费率高、门槛高、期限长等缺点，投资境外保险产品如香港保险，对中国内地居民而言是最明智的投资选择。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8950,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492766765000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Jessica","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny69VF5hyBCTTzSa8wPTHaRoaOjzqWoOPA6LfVz3mptgVmJLGdicRv3OckQtSu2JiaawRZJ7VyTpIAfFQ/0","content":"<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">1. 9月份，购买美元理财产品比购买人民币理财产品收益率要高。</span><div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">2. 投资美元存款和美元理财有助于资产保值，但对投资者把握外汇走势较高，还是需要谨慎选择。</span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">3. 第四季度，人民币继续贬值。有一些投资者在2015年就发现了人民币的这种潜质，开始配置境外资产。</span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">4. 虽然境外资产可以有效避免人民币贬值的风险，但是由于有些境外投资的门槛较高，还是存在很大风险的。</span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">5. 配置香港保险对于想要避免人民币贬值的投资者来说无疑是相对稳妥的方式。</span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><br></span></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8944,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492765745000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"敏","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay36u84xJJa5xZVbSorVQsjiaRtdKff23d2pibDW0oSbVW3r0CUiaQtIg47Itf131L8acNXmLucqib4ibt/0","content":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">人民币存在贬值风险，可考虑购买美元理财。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">优势：</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">1.升值趋势明显，扣除换汇费率，平均收益更高。</span></p><p><font color=\"#333333\" style=\"font-family: 华文细黑, Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 微软雅黑, 'Microsoft YaHei UI', SimSun, SimHei, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 19px; line-height: 30.4px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">需考虑因素</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">1.长期持有更有利。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">2.起投要求15万以上。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">3.要</span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">有</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">把握外汇走势的能力。</span></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">综上，境外保险特别是香港保险，更值得投资，可以降低纯人民币资产组合的风险。</span></font></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">PS:题外话，之前看过一篇保险业介绍文章。香港保险的要求和国内要求不同，要求更低，购买风险更高。</span></font></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8933,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492764232000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"林燕忠","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/hglMZuicA3iauTIlciaKXMtjCVHiczz6BaGSFgickVX9JuklyB6UnDVicrcDBdpG7JicTRHGib5qEs5BicEcWOiaGEVZ3htc8bYMbob3q7/0","content":"<img src=\"http://static.iqycamp.com/application-20170421144911-h05czv9p7-.JPG\" style=\"max-width: 90%; -webkit-touch-callout: none; -webkit-user-select: none;\"><br>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8908,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492757354000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"夏薇","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/0V44XKgFuKBM9EQCeEfs2HUMCa2icXS15wy3GNwLUdliastu7ZqUcM6XCCJUybGDApzO8O2eIyApz0tmcg8cdibALfK5pU0Fiaiaw/0","content":"<font color=\"#000000\" size=\"3\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);\">数据显示，9月份发行的人民币理财产品平均收益率为3.7%，美元理财产品平均收益率为1.57%，如果算上美元近一年升值6%的优势，即使扣去0.4%的换汇成本，购买美元理财产品比购买人民币理财产品收益率要高。</span></font>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8801,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492735463000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"倩然","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny68SBuoLQ2thBI8GibibHnUMvT9hXtx6dwp9AG7pnQQIBPLb7GrdetpTibQHSOmbO3mWQ2lCBvlPHq4EC9FIQiceymmw/0","content":"人民币贬值，把钱存在银行里相当于赔钱。<div>从数据分析，购买美元理财产品比人民币收益高，但是美元投资产品预期收益率还是比国内理财产品低。外汇投资周期长，利率波动大，投资需要谨慎。</div><div>境外资产配置例如境外保险的购买相对其他理财产品稳妥一些。</div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8783,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492732314000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"ly","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay8SjSiao9Mmc4WpXwqIADiaaB7kcG06hoxmH9vpvHeOhdyAWzk8ydeBkL8Wictm9vPaBEvkvCmWWUWg/0","content":"1. 由于CPI的影响，在银行存钱的结果是贬值<div>2. 理财投资产品抗贬值能力较高，但选择原则应按照自己的情况分析</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; 短期少量优选港资保险</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; 长期或大量，在分析足够后选择境外保险</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8745,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492708620000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Scipio","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoEPiaBIMUZPQ0G8A2lpWYnWMCFWETxaCfCNwvQLfbOUNkibNAclBSK8LTYGpPcLxRX95HP2iaAt9z5p/0","content":"<div>在国内，把钱存在银行相当于赔钱，所以建议配置海外投资产品。</div><div>海外投资产品中，美元投资类产品门槛较高，一般在15万美元以上，且投资期限较长。</div><div>外汇投资类产品投资周期相对较长。</div><div>境外保险产品相对与其他的理财产品而言比较稳妥一点。</div><div>与中国内地居民而言，配置香港保险无疑是最佳的选择。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8743,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492708298000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"less is more","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyicEOWYLDZMEh0H2lcHzvdCLQZ4wJpibQgsLia6u7UbDRJFSLJbjDQiapPd1UicPCWMUDqsHDvGZnwcdia/0","content":"<div>综合比较内地、海外投资、理财产品，配置香港保险是最佳选择</div>1、美元理财产品比人民币理财产品收益率高，但因投资者要求较高，需谨慎购买；<div>2、人民币有贬值风险，存在银行相当于赔钱；</div><div>3、海外投资收益低，外汇投资周期长，均有缺陷；</div><div>4、境外保险产品相对其他理财比较稳妥。<br><div><br></div></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8728,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492704477000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"寂静欢喜\uD83C\uDF88","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay8uWyib00wYicO2J9P7L9CxiaVZm3mOm6M3HF1jWfCyK4feddMLIA8o74wNibFU244cGO17ZEich7WYjB/0","content":"人民币的理财收益率在3.7％，中国CPI增幅连续4个月超过1％所以把钱放在银行理财里还是赔钱<div>美元理财收益率在1.57％扣初0.4的换汇成本加之6％的收益率看似高过人民币理财产品其实不然美元投资门槛较高。金额大时间长有一定的风险实则回报低于人民币投资。</div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px;\">在这种形式下更适合做境外保险产品相对与其他的理财产品而言比较稳妥一点。与中国内地居民而言，配置香港保险无疑是最佳的选择。</span><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8689,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492701333000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"橙子 ","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoGTEYGQCXrBqNrQBQR9pSe4rdfDOCjoCmibCnA0yuMjqBSmN1nVXuiaAw9Zv7L1apqiaSuuUvAFCCHS/0","content":"<ol><li>（经济背景）就我国最近的通胀率，钱存银行只能坐等贬值。所以需要进行合理理财投资。</li><li>（外币资产的收益）国内理财产品收益尽管将近4%，但今年外币很可能升值6%，就算再加上手续费，配置国外资产还是很有赚头！</li><li>（外币资产的风险）然而，像海外投资类产品期限长，门槛高，汇率又一直在波动，所以对于咱老百姓来说，风险比较高。</li><li>（结论）相对来讲，境外保险相对来讲风险小，门槛低，又能搭上外币升值的顺风车，对咱来讲，是性价比最高的选择！</li></ol>","voteCount":1,"comm